2009-04-20  Nick Williams

	* Release: 2.0.0
	- refactor, new functionality of optional 'takeover'

2009-04-20  Nick Williams

	* Release: 2.0.0
	- Upgrade PAN syntax to v8
	- Upgrade component to use LC::Check and LC::File for reading/writing
	  instead of using hand-rolled versions.
	- provide "takeover" flag (defaults to false for backwards compatibility)
	  which indicates if manually managed hosts can be "taken over" by this
	  component instead of leaving them alone.
	- line ordering based on hostname is preserved, instead of
	  sorting alphabetically.

